Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大戰中戰死者的墓碑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把這些全都找一遍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先找到地圖上標注的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和望一郎的墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好像發生過戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對死者也該有所敬重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對死者敬重？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是魔王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在不是魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來也不會是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你是魔王才看上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你是個這麼沒趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…你想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話等會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去  然後忘掉這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則小心小命不保
